name: The world does not need you to save it!
description:
How mighty is our ego, how high have you chosen to put yourself on a pedestal, wherein your right mind did you register that it is okay to save the world, it is logically, and scientifically by design, built to care for itself, and those that live amongst it

So why do we go on about saving the world? Why do we fight so much to save a world that is by design built to protect itself, "it will be here long after we are going"

read more at https://ipfs.io/ipfs/Qmf2f1eSigrdhJr3kYN5sVoJ3F6FfyhZ6ZyMTL1U7HiBSb?filename=the%20world%20does%20not%20need%20saving.edited.docx
